<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Anchor Up - Logo Concept</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f8ff 0%, #e6f2ff 100%);
            color: #333;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(10, 36, 99, 0.15);
            padding: 40px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            padding-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e9f5ff;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            color: #0A2463;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .header p {
            color: #2A9D8F;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .logo-presentation {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }
        
        .logo-option {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
            background: #f9fdff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(10, 36, 99, 0.08);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .logo-option:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(10, 36, 99, 0.12);
        }
        
        .logo-option h2 {
            color: #0A2463;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #2A9D8F;
        }
        
        .logo-display {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .logo-a {
            /* Stacked layout */
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .logo-b {
            /* Inline layout */
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        
        .logo-c {
            /* Circular emblem */
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .anchor-icon {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .anchor-icon-up {
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(-5deg); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-5px) rotate(0deg); }
        }
        
        .anchor-shape {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .anchor-shank {
            position: absolute;
            width: 8px;
            height: 60px;
            background-color: #0A2463;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            top: 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        .anchor-ring {
            position: absolute;
            width: 22px;
            height: 22px;
            border: 5px solid #E9C46A;
            border-radius: 50%;
            top: -5px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        .anchor-fluke-left {
            position: absolute;
            width: 40px;
            height: 20px;
            background-color: #0A2463;
            border-radius: 4px 20px 4px 4px;
            bottom: 15px;
            left: 5px;
            transform: rotate(30deg);
        }
        
        .anchor-fluke-right {
            position: absolute;
            width: 40px;
            height: 20px;
            background-color: #0A2463;
            border-radius: 20px 4px 4px 4px;
            bottom: 15px;
            right: 5px;
            transform: rotate(-30deg);
        }
        
        .anchor-fluke-up {
            bottom: 25px;
            transform: rotate(45deg);
            background-color: #2A9D8F;
        }
        
        .rope {
            position: absolute;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border: 3px solid #E9C46A;
            border-top: none;
            border-right: none;
            border-radius: 0 0 0 40px;
            top: -15px;
            left: -5px;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .logo-text {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .logo-text-inline {
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: baseline;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .anchor-text {
            color: #0A2463;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .up-text {
            color: #2A9D8F;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            position: relative;
            top: -5px;
        }
        
        .emblem-circle {
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 8px solid #0A2463;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(10, 36, 99, 0.15);
        }
        
        .emblem-rope-border {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 4px dashed #E9C46A;
            top: -4px;
            left: -4px;
        }
        
        .emblem-text {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            color: #0A2463;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        .emblem-main {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .emblem-sub {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #2A9D8F;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .wave-line {
            width: 120px;
            height: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .wave {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, #2A9D8F 50%, transparent 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
        
        .color-palette {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .palette-title {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #0A2463;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .colors {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .color-swatch {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .color-navy {
            background-color: #0A2463;
        }
        
        .color-teal {
            background-color: #2A9D8F;
        }
        
        .color-gold {
            background-color: #E9C46A;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .color-white {
            background-color: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .applications {
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        
        .applications h2 {
            color: #0A2463;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }
        
        .app-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }
        
        .app-item {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(10, 36, 99, 0.08);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .app-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #2A9D8F;
        }
        
        .app-item h3 {
            color: #0A2463;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
        
        .app-item p {
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e9f5ff;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 25px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }
            
            .logo-option {
                min-width: 100%;
            }
            
            .logo-b {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }
            
            .logo-text-inline {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Anchor Up Logo Concept</h1>
            <p>Boat Chartering Company - Nautical & Modern Design</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="logo-presentation">
            <div class="logo-option">
                <h2>Option A: Stacked Layout</h2>
                <div class="logo-display">
                    <div class="logo-a">
                        <div class="anchor-icon anchor-icon-up">
                            <div class="rope"></div>
                            <div class="anchor-shape">
                                <div class="anchor-ring"></div>
                                <div class="anchor-shank"></div>
                                <div class="anchor-fluke-left anchor-fluke-up"></div>
                                <div class="anchor-fluke-right"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="logo-text">
                            <div class="anchor-text">ANCHOR</div>
                            <div class="up-text">UP</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="wave-line">
                            <div class="wave"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> Website headers, business cards, and signage. Clean and modern with clear hierarchy.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="logo-option">
                <h2>Option B: Inline Layout</h2>
                <div class="logo-display">
                    <div class="logo-b">
                        <div class="anchor-icon">
                            <div class="anchor-shape">
                                <div class="anchor-ring"></div>
                                <div class="anchor-shank"></div>
                                <div class="anchor-fluke-left"></div>
                                <div class="anchor-fluke-right"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="logo-text logo-text-inline">
                            <div class="anchor-text">ANCHOR</div>
                            <div class="up-text">UP</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> App icons, social media profiles, and promotional materials. Compact and recognizable.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="logo-option">
                <h2>Option C: Circular Emblem</h2>
                <div class="logo-display">
                    <div class="logo-c">
                        <div class="emblem-circle">
                            <div class="emblem-rope-border"></div>
                            <div class="anchor-icon">
                                <div class="anchor-shape">
                                    <div class="anchor-ring"></div>
                                    <div class="anchor-shank"></div>
                                    <div class="anchor-fluke-left"></div>
                                    <div class="anchor-fluke-right"></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="emblem-text">
                                <div class="emblem-main">ANCHOR UP</div>
                                <div class="emblem-sub">BOAT CHARTER</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> Boat flags, apparel, and merchandise. Classic nautical badge style.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="color-palette">
            <div class="palette-title">Color Palette</div>
            <div class="colors">
                <div class="color-swatch color-navy">Navy<br>#0A2463</div>
                <div class="color-swatch color-teal">Teal<br>#2A9D8F</div>
                <div class="color-swatch color-gold">Gold<br>#E9C46A</div>
                <div class="color-swatch color-white">White</div>
            </div>
            <p>Colors represent trust (navy), the sea (teal), luxury/quality (gold), and cleanliness (white).</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="applications">
            <h2>Potential Applications</h2>
            <div class="app-grid">
                <div class="app-item">
                    <div class="app-icon"><i class="fas fa-ship"></i></div>
                    <h3>Boat Flags & Decals</h3>
                    <p>Emblem style works perfectly for boat flags, hull decals, and nautical equipment.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="app-item">
                    <div class="app-icon"><i class="fas fa-desktop"></i></div>
                    <h3>Website & App</h3>
                    <p>Stacked and inline logos adapt well to digital platforms with clean scalability.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="app-item">
                    <div class="app-icon"><i class="fas fa-tshirt"></i></div>
                    <h3>Crew Apparel</h3>
                    <p>Professional branding for staff uniforms, hats, and promotional clothing.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="app-item">
                    <div class="app-icon"><i class="fas fa-receipt"></i></div>
                    <h3>Marketing Materials</h3>
                    <p>Brochures, business cards, and signage that convey trust and professionalism.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Anchor Up Logo Concept | Designed for Boat Chartering Company</p>
            <p>All design elements are conceptual and can be refined for final production.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <script>
        // Add subtle interactive effects
        document.querySelectorAll('.logo-option').forEach(option => {
            option.addEventListener('mouseenter', function() {
                const anchor = this.querySelector('.anchor-icon');
                if(anchor) {
                    anchor.classList.add('anchor-icon-up');
                }
            });
            
            option.addEventListener('mouseleave', function() {
                const anchor = this.querySelector('.anchor-icon');
                if(anchor) {
                    anchor.classList.remove('anchor-icon-up');
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
